---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Intimacy of Light | The Subtle Shift">
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="laurel">
                <img src="/images/laurel.svg" alt="Laurel" class="laurel-image">
                <span class="laurel-text">Denise's<br>First book!</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="section-title">The Intimacy of Light</h1>
            <p class="section-description">A Journey of Multidimensionality and Divine Love</p>
        </div>

        <div class="book-page-content">
            <div class="book-showcase">
                <div class="book-image-large">
                    <img src="/images/intimacy-of-light.png" alt="The Intimacy of Light book cover">
                </div>
                <div class="book-details">
                    <h2>About the Book</h2>
                    <p class="book-description">This book is a deeply personal story of spiritual awakening. It is a captivating blend of <strong>cosmic memoir</strong> and <strong>spiritual guidebook</strong>, in which Denise Benning (Channa Dee) shares the journey of her soul's light, guided by the radiant presence of Jeremiah, a Divine Master with whom she shares an eternal connection spanning countless lifetimes.</p>
                    
                    <p>Through intimate revelations and profound teachings, readers are invited to explore their own multidimensional nature and the infinite love that connects us all. This book offers both inspiration and practical guidance for those seeking to deepen their spiritual understanding and connection to the divine.</p>

                    <div class="book-features">
                        <h3>What You'll Discover</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>The nature of multidimensional existence</li>
                            <li>How to connect with your spiritual guides</li>
                            <li>Understanding past life connections and soul contracts</li>
                            <li>The power of light language and energy healing</li>
                            <li>Practical exercises for spiritual development</li>
                            <li>Messages of hope and divine love</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="book-retailers">
                        <h3>Available Now</h3>
                        <div class="retailer-links">
                            <a href="https://www.amazon.com" class="book-retailer" aria-label="Amazon" target="_blank">
                                <img src="/images/amazon-logo-squid-ink-smile-orange.png" alt="Amazon">
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://books.apple.com" class="book-retailer" aria-label="Apple Books" target="_blank">
                                <img src="/images/Download_on_Apple-books.png" alt="Apple Books">
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://www.kobo.com" class="book-retailer" aria-label="Kobo" target="_blank">
                                <img src="/images/Kobo-logo.png" alt="Kobo">
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://www.kindle.com" class="book-retailer" aria-label="Kindle" target="_blank">
                                <img src="/images/amazon-kindle-logo.png" alt="Kindle">
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="book-testimonials">
                <h3>What Readers Are Saying</h3>
                <div class="book-testimonial-grid">
                    <blockquote class="book-testimonial">
                        <p>"A beautiful and transformative read that opened my heart to new possibilities. Denise's journey is both deeply personal and universally relevant."</p>
                        <cite>— Sarah M.</cite>
                    </blockquote>
                    <blockquote class="book-testimonial">
                        <p>"The Intimacy of Light is more than a book—it's a spiritual experience. I found myself connecting with my own guides in ways I never thought possible."</p>
                        <cite>— Michael R.</cite>
                    </blockquote>
                    <blockquote class="book-testimonial">
                        <p>"Denise's vulnerability and wisdom shine through every page. This book has become a treasured companion on my spiritual journey."</p>
                        <cite>— Jennifer L.</cite>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="book-author">
                <h3>About the Author</h3>
                <div class="author-content">
                    <div class="author-image">
                        <img src="/images/ALG_7865.jpeg" alt="Denise Benning">
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-bio">
                        <p>Denise Benning (Channa Dee) is an energy healer, divine channel, author, and intuitive dedicated to guiding individuals on a journey of self-discovery and soul connection. With a unique background as an Olympian figure skater and over 15 years of experience in spiritual guidance, Denise brings both discipline and divine wisdom to her work.</p>
                        
                        <p>She offers transformative healing sessions and hosts spiritual events at her rustic retreat in the woods of Trent Lakes, Ontario, providing a sanctuary for those seeking inner peace and renewal.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="book-cta">
                <h3>Ready to Begin Your Journey?</h3>
                <p>Get your copy of "The Intimacy of Light" today and discover the profound connection between your soul and the divine.</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com" class="button button-primary" target="_blank">Order Now</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="button button-outline">Connect with Denise</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
</Layout> 